[This Game Requires A PS2 Code Breaker V7.0 Or Higher!\Super Weapon Modifier]
author=Code Master
description=This code allows you to equip any weapon for any character. When you are at the screen before you start a level where you choose your weapons, items, save, etc.. Hold R1 to start cycling your Equipped weapon until you get to the one you want. If you pass up the weapon you want, hold L1 to go back.
